('68028542e3c98b0941766116', '老品牌，颇有底蕴的酒店。给人富丽贵气的感觉。喜欢酒店礼宾部Gary小陈的介绍。相比之下，四楼博物馆门口小哥的态度很让人费解，一个酒店博物馆不就是为了推介吸引参观吗，什么要预约扫码，还不对住客有专享，你以为自己专属文旅就可以这种态度对宾客？搞笑了，让人没胃口看了。', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232912000eeukd8tE6EC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234m12000eeuykg08A8A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234212000eeusgqaED6C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236112000eeuu2yu211E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236y12000eeun32b26AB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232m12000eev28rd1C03_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236z12000eeuvc5w69E5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 4.8, 4, '2024-06-10', '花园双床房', '双床房', '家庭亲子', 131, 0, 54, 8, '["前台服务","整体满意度"]'::jsonb, '前台服务', '整体满意度', NULL),
('68028542e3c98b0941766117', '在ARIEL的帮不下我带着外国客人顺利入住了酒店 大家都觉得这是人生中住过最豪华和友善的酒店 房间很舒服 设施也好 绿化一流 再次感谢ARIEL的帮助', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235q12000ehu5f77E7E2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233s12000ehu351r2DF4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230112000ehub5hg66FE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231t12000ehu9kjv005E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233g12000ehu4jwn2586_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232l12000ehu29ooA211_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230612000ehu4mcrD570_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231f12000ehu10of8A1C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233p12000ehu9oo24A01_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 5, 5, '2024-06-16', '花园大床房', '大床房', '商务出差', 75, 0, 29, 6, '["整体满意度","前台服务","房间设施"]'::jsonb, '整体满意度', '前台服务', '房间设施'),
('68028542e3c98b0941766118', '非常舒适的酒店，地理位置极佳。出门地铁5号线淘金站，去哪儿都方便。酒店服务很好，周到细致。送至房间的点心贴心。喜欢二楼的荔湾庭早午茶，味道好、环境佳，性价比高。', '["https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232312000egcia5eBE4D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235r12000egceakk4685_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231512000egcftibFD44_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235m12000egcdckv0B14_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232812000egbzayx3C56_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231b12000egcuxem9CC3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234t12000egc8s5y8FAA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236012000egcl4auAE51_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg","https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231612000egcbrwqBFC6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg"]'::jsonb, 5, 5, '2024-06-12', '花园大床房', '大床房', '家庭亲子', 80, 0, 54, 9, '["交通便利性","餐饮设施","整体满意度"]'::jsonb, '交通便利性', '餐饮设施', '整体满意度'),
